BLIN The StochasticMomentumIndex is at 91 on the Weekly chart Thats the lowest its ever been in its history The second lowest was in Nov of 2018 88 It took a month and a 25 drop with bullish divergence before went up 40 in 2 days Thats just one indicator but it makes you wonder when this is going to spike Im guessing it will spike enough for bag holders to bail in a month if they can hold out for another 25 down The StochasticMomentumIndex is at 63 on the Daily chart and has been bouncing in the oversold area since the end of April Thats the longest it has ever stayed in the oversold area Im ignore everything that happened before the big volume spike in May That volume is exponentially larger than anything in the past Its an IPO Start date May of 2019
